{"tid":2259944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大揀院長學生代表民選或變委任 校長盡拎所有權力成「港大皇帝」","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T09:34:24.000Z","uid":344792,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"76dfb080bdd5fc18b7cf97ee37fda0a642de413d","tid":2259944,"uid":344792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"【XGU】港大今日校委會會議後 揀院長學生代表民選或變委任 校長盡拎所有權力成「港大皇帝」<br />\n<br />\n港大校委會今日開會將審議兩名副校長的人事任命。但《加山傳播》經可靠消息獲悉，週二港大校委會議程上，除了副校長任命外，亦將審議一系列港大的政策和人事架構的變動&mdash;&mdash;包括將院務委員會主席從院長覓選委員會中剔除，而以往民選的學生和教師代表亦將轉為校長委任。同時以往就院長續約，校長要諮詢掌管所有校務的「中央管理小組」，但今日會議擬將條文刪除，以係院長續任由校長自行決定，形成中央集權。<br />\n<br />\n詳細報導內容: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Hu21EE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Hu21EE&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=832f5f52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Hu21EE</a><br />\n<br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #香港 #政治 #香港大學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/362927128457026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109301110486297%2Fposts%2F362927128457026%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=36333aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/362927128457026/</a>"},{"pid":"a4bf3b46ccd3989d77730160a1847649f8ed8418","tid":2259944,"uid":344792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNNZPpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNNZPpK.jpg&h=9a95d401&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1OMDkwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1OMDkwq.jpg&h=ecf84962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bumvV4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbumvV4M.jpg&h=4af37570&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbCCA4N.jpg\" data-thu